::Aerotaur::
       "I'd be happy to Nightlight, it would be my pleasure."  He bows his 
head slightly and walks off past Nightlight and Flicker holding Elita close 
to his body.  He coos softly in her ear and walks to Rodimus's chambers to 
put Elita down for a nap and look for Rodimus.  With her safely in her crib 
he opens a com link to Kup.  "Sir, I was wondering if you could tell me where 
Rodimus is.  I checked his chambers but he's not here.  Nightlight asked me 
to tell him that she's waiting for him.  She was leaving on a mission with 
Flicker I believe."

--part1_126.25cd1db2.2bb26a35_boundary
